pycutest.print_available_sif_params¶

pycutest.print_available_sif_params(problemName)¶

Call sifdecode on given problem to print out available parameters This function is OS dependent. Currently works only for Linux and MacOS.

Parameters

problemName – CUTEst problem name

Returns

Nothing
